headline: Is It Too Late To Consider DaVita (DVA) After Its Sharp 30 Day Surge
summary: For investors considering whether DaVita at around US$150.73 represents attractive value or appears expensive after its recent run, this article focuses on what the current price could mean for long-term investors.
